---
title: Messy Spiced Paneer Wraps with Mango Chutney and Pickled Onions
description: Sweet and spicy: there's no better pair! Sticky sweet mango chutney is delicious drizzled over curry-coated nuggets of paneer. Perky red onions add pickled tang to the wrap and a tomato side salad!
